Class FieldTypeInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.hadoop.record.meta.FieldTypeInfo

public class FieldTypeInfo
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a type information for a field, which is made up of its ID (name) and its type (a TypeID object).
